-= Kitchen =-
You are in a kitchen. A normal one.

You make out a closed fridge. You make out an oven, so there's that. You see a table. Wow, isn't TextWorld just the best? On the table you see a cookbook and a knife. Classic TextWorld. Look out! It's a- oh, never mind, it's just a counter. On the counter you see a raw red potato, a raw purple potato, a red onion and a raw yellow potato. Suddenly, you bump your head on the ceiling, but it's not such a bad bump that it's going to prevent you from looking at objects and even things. Look over there! a stove. The stove is conventional. But oh no! there's nothing on this piece of garbage.
